block_list.title: Video Tutorial
block_list.body: This is Paper plane 21 of our 100 Exotic Paper Airplane Challenge. The Simple Dart by John Smith. This is an origami plane folded from a square sheet. If you missed my last Exotic Paper Airplane "Paper Plane 020 : Ready For Takeoff by Didier Boursin ", you could watch it at https://youtu.be/gvoPPkv6roo Thanks for watching! Wilson Lee @Heap Art
